    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:64ch;">The same operating standard and Certified ProAdvisor delivery, with each industry&rsquo;s real New York angle.</p>
    <div class="r-2">
      {%- for c in moreIndustries %}
      <a class="rel-card" href="{{ c.href }}"><h3 class="rel-card__t">{{ c.name | safe }}</h3><p class="rel-card__d">{{ c.angle | safe }}</p><span class="ptier__link" style="margin-top:10px;">Explore &rarr;</span></a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="prose" style="margin-top:22px;"><p><small>{{ moreNote | safe }}</small></p></div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── EXPERT REVIEW · firm-level, no founder name (H2: Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-hub-review">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Page review &amp; standards</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.</h2>
    <div class="byline" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:18px;">
      <div class="byline__mark" aria-hidden="true" style="width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:9px;background:var(--color-accent);flex:none;"></div>
      <div>
        <p class="byline__name" style="margin:0;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-ink);">By the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team</p>
        <p class="byline__review" style="margin:2px 0 0;">TechBrot Inc. &middot; Independent Certified ProAdvisor firm</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Maintained by the accounting team at <strong>TechBrot Inc.</strong>, a Delaware-incorporated independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm serving New York businesses across all 62 counties, and reviewed for technical accuracy across the industries represented here &mdash; including New York-specific rules (legal <a href="https://www.iola.org/" rel="noopener nofollow">IOLTA</a> trust accounting, nonprofit <a href="https://www.charitiesnys.com/" rel="noopener nofollow">CHAR500</a>, and NYC sales tax per the <a href="https://www.tax.ny.gov/" rel="noopener nofollow">NY Department of Taxation &amp; Finance</a>). TechBrot delivers the books and coordinates with your CPA, who files.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-row">
      {%- for c in reviewCreds %}
      <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value" style="font-size:15px;">{{ c.label }}</p><p class="trust-row__label">{{ c.detail | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- if not loop.last %}<div class="trust-row__divider"></div>{%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="meta-reviewed"><span>Published: 2026-06-07</span><span>Updated: 2026-06-07</span><span>Reviewed: 2026-06-07 &middot; Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor</span></p>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── RELATED · next-step rel-cards; each H3 verbatim (H2: Related New York services. + 4 H3s) ── #}
